OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778609470
OL,3,CTwelfth member of religious group
OL,4,Carrested as investigations continue
OL,6,FA twelfth person has been arrested as
OL,7,Fpart of an ongoing investigation into
OL,8,Fserious offences allegedly involving
OL,9,Fmembers of a religious group in Crewe.
OL,11,FCheshire Police confirmed that a 30-
OL,12,Fyear-old Mexican national was detained
OL,13,Fin Croydon on Friday 8 May, on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of sexual assault by
OL,15,Fpenetration and modern slavery
OL,16,Foffences.
OL,18,FHe has since been interviewed and
OL,19,Freleased on conditional bail.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
