OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778609470
OL,3,CTwelfth member of religious group
OL,4,Carrested as investigations continue
OL,6,FPolice are applying for a Slavery and
OL,7,FTrafficking Risk Order, with a court
OL,8,Fhearing set for next week.
OL,10,FThe arrest follows the arrest of a 48-
OL,11,Fyear-old British national a day
OL,12,Fearlier, who has also been bailed and
OL,13,Fis subject to a Slavery and
OL,14,FTrafficking Risk Order.
OL,16,FThe investigation began in March 2026
OL,17,Fafter police received reports of
OL,18,Fserious sexual offences, forced
OL,19,Fmarriage, and modern slavery involving
OL,20,Fmembers of the Ahmadi Religion of
OL,21,FPeace and Light group.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
