FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778609470
OL,3,CTwelfth member of religious group
OL,4,Carrested as investigations continue
OL,6,FThe alleged offences occurred in 2023
OL,7,Fand involved one victim, a woman who
OL,8,Fwas a member of the group at the time.
OL,10,FAnd on April 19, officers executed
OL,11,Fthree warrants in Crewe, arresting six
OL,12,Fmen and three women on suspicion of
OL,13,Foffences including rape, human
OL,14,Ftrafficking, modern slavery, sexual
OL,15,Fassault, and forced marriage.
OL,17,FAll have since been released on
OL,18,Fconditional bail.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
