PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778609470
OL,3,CTwelfth member of religious group
OL,4,Carrested as investigations continue
OL,6,FSuperintendent Adam Waller said: "This
OL,7,Finvestigation is still very much
OL,8,Factive and remains at a fast pace.
OL,10,F"While all the suspects we have
OL,11,Farrested are members of the group, as
OL,12,Fwe have stated from the beginning,
OL,13,Fthis is not an investigation into the
OL,14,Freligion. Our investigation solely
OL,15,Ffocuses on the serious allegations
OL,16,Fwhich have been reported to us."
